    "actor": "https://uofa.net/synth/actor/morrison-credibility-assessment-team",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 13 credibility factors reviewed against MRL 5 requirements. Seven factors were formally assessed; all seven exhibit achieved levels below required levels. Six factors were flagged as not-assessed epistemic gaps. Despite these gaps, the package is accepted for submission under the Minimal profile, which does not mandate resolution of all factor gaps prior to regulatory submission — it requires documentation of the current credibility state. The assessment team acknowledges that the package does not meet the substantive credibility threshold for regulatory acceptance of the device claim and recommends a gap-closure plan before resubmission under the Complete profile.",
